Dj McCoy is a traditional Hip-Hop DJ & he's been down with the turntables & representing since 1986. If you are into the wide range of late 80's 'till mid 90's Hip-Hop acts you will propably bounce your head to this funky & stylish mix made in good old HH traditions.

You'll get everything from Whodini,Krs-1, Q-tip,Marley Marl,Salt n Pepa,Arrested Devolepment To Eric B & Rakim,2Pac,NWA,Lords Of The Underground,Apace Indian, Das Efx and Geto Boys + lots of other ill shit.
